node.text:
The Jaw Dropping @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron TourBillon Baguette in 6 different Variations. 🔥 Which one would you pick? 
The Bugatti Chiron TourBillon has many guises, including Bugatti Chiron TourBillon Baguette Black and Orange Sapphires - the spirit of the Chiron captured in a timepiece. 

The case is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron and the movement, or “engine block,” intended to duplicate the Bugatti engine, is placed  under a massive sapphire crystal, on display for to all to see. With to push of right-hand crown of the timepiece the engine comes to life, just like a true internal combustion engine. The movement is comprised of 578 components). #jacobandco

node.text:
ENGINE ON! The @jacobandco BUGATTI Chiron Tourbillon Rose Gold has a 55mm-by-45mm case made of highly polished 18K rose gold. Its tonneau shape is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron hyper sports car, giving it a sleek, aerodynamic appearance. Inside is a replica of the BUGATTI 16-cylinder engine visible through sapphire crystal. 

The engine is suspended within the watch case by four pillars that look like Chiron shock absorbers. Activated on demand, the “engine” comes to life with 16 pistons pumping and two turbochargers spinning. In addition, there’s a 30° inclined 60-second flying tourbillon visible through the horseshoe-shaped BUGATTI grill on the front of the case.

Watch technology at the highest level: three crowns for the watch are at the back of the case in a dashboard display. The left stem sets the time, the middle winds the movement and separate engine animation, and the right crown starts the animation. The watch is powered by the JCAM37 mechanical movement with a 60-hour power reserve. The power-reserve indicator is visible at 9 o’clock.

#BUGATTI #JACOBANDCO #JACOBANDCOBUGATTI

node.text:
@jacobandco Shows building a fully working automotive engine, a one-minute flying tourbillon inclined at a 30-degree angle, and several other components of aesthetic and technical mastery, and placing them inside a tonneau-shaped watch is a horological achievement. The Bugatti Chiron timepiece is a tribute to the hyper sportscar of the same name. It replicates the high-performance automobile, not only in its appearance, but in its fine design and high watchmaking craftsmanship.

After a year of development, @jacobandco and Bugatti created the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon, a watch unlike no other. The tonneau-shaped case of the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon is inspired by the flowing lines of the Chiron hyper sportscar, giving it a sleek, aerodynamic appearance. Beneath the sapphire crystal is a fully working Bugatti W16 car engine that operates on demand. It's a groundbreaking concept that emulates the speed and beauty of the Chiron. #jacobandco #sapphire
